node.text:
Head over to the @CenterConsolesOnly YouTube channel for the full @SeaVeeBoatsOfficial Virtual Boat Show event schedule.  We will be unveiling their flagship 450z and covering each model in the Sea Vee lineup individually.  It won’t stop there... we’ll be chatting with @mercurymarine, @furuno_usa, @seakeeper_inc and @jlaudioinc about their collaboration on the 450z.  You won’t want to miss this!
-
https://www.youtube.com/c/CenterConsolesOnly
-
#CenterConsolesOnly #SeaVeeBoats #VirtualBoatShow

node.title: Virtual Boat Show featuring the new 450Z
